fields.title: Personalized Laser Engraved Metal Buckle Dog Collar
fields.description: These Personalized dog collars are 100% handmade in the US! They are durable due to the zinc alloy metal buckle, slide-adjuster and large gauge D-ring, as well as our soft, yet heavyweight COTTON canvas webbing strap that measures 1 1/4 inch wide. We ensure a long-lasting collar and are also 100% satisfaction guaranteed. These custom pet collars are laser-engraved on the the font of your metal buckle; the text will appear matte white/light gray as seen in the photos.
